NOTICE — PAPER TRADING ONLY
---------------------------
This software was produced as part of an undergraduate research project
(UMBC URCAD) studying the behavior of large language models in simulated
financial markets. It is intended for use ONLY with paper trading accounts.

The authors do NOT endorse, recommend, or warrant the use of any code in
this repository with live brokerage funds. Nothing in this repository is
financial advice. Consult a licensed financial advisor before making any
real-money investment decisions.

See DISCLAIMER.md for the full notice.
